OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FA cleanup operation is underway in
OL,7,FSouthampton after protesters clashed
OL,8,Fwith police on Tuesday night, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Jonathan Swain reports
OL,11,FMinisters have appealed for calm after
OL,12,Fviolent clashes between protesters and
OL,13,Fpolice near where Henry Nowak was
OL,14,Fstabbed to death.
OL,16,FTwo people were arrested for
OL,17,Fassaulting police and possession of a
OL,18,Fweapon, after hundreds gathered
OL,19,Foutside Southampton Central Police
OL,20,FStation on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
