PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FTommy Robinson - real name Stephen
OL,7,FYaxley-Lennon - and campaigner
OL,8,FLaurence Fox were among those who
OL,9,Fspoke to the crowd.
OL,11,FThe unrest came amid an outcry about
OL,12,Fthe policing response to the murder
OL,13,Fafter the university student's killer
OL,14,Fclaimed he had been the victim of a
OL,15,Fracial attack while Mr Nowak was
OL,16,Fhandcuffed by police as he lay dying.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
