OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,7,F(NPCC) announced it would review anti-
OL,8,Fracism guidance - which advises police
OL,9,Fto treat ethnic minorities differently
OL,10,Fto get them better outcomes - that
OL,11,Fsome have blamed for the actions of
OL,12,Fthe officers who arrested Mr Nowak.
OL,14,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said she
OL,15,Funderstood the anger the case had
OL,16,Fcaused, but urged people not to "over-
OL,17,Freact", saying Mr Nowak's family did
OL,18,Fnot want his murder to stir up
OL,19,Fhostility or division.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,F"We are urging that people take the
OL,7,Fanger that they feel, which I
OL,8,Funderstand, but let's allow justice to
OL,9,Fdo its course, and let's not over-
OL,10,Freact, which indeed is what the family
OL,11,Fare asking us to do as well," she told
OL,12,FTimes Radio.
OL,14,FMs Jones defended the police's Race
OL,15,FAction Plan, although ministers have
OL,16,Facknowledged that wording in a police
OL,17,Fcommitment document alongside it is
OL,18,F"clumsy".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FShe said "everyone must be equal under
OL,7,Fthe law and we must ensure that is the
OL,8,Fcase", but "we can't shy away from
OL,9,Fwhat are historic and legitimate
OL,10,Fconcerns about racism within police
OL,11,Fforces".
OL,13,FNPCC chairman Gavin Stephens said: "We
OL,14,Fare listening to legitimate concerns
OL,15,Fabout how some of these commitments
OL,16,Fare worded or phrased, and where
OL,17,Fneeded we can and will make changes,
OL,18,Fbut this should not detract from the
OL,19,Fintent, which is to improve the
OL,20,Fquality of policing."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FThe case has been seized on by
OL,7,Fpoliticians including Nigel Farage,
OL,8,Fpolitical activist Tommy Robinson and
OL,9,Ftech billionaire Elon Musk.
OL,11,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch said
OL,12,F"pernicious identity politics" had
OL,13,Fseen the country "going backwards".
OL,15,FIn a Daily Mail article, she said
OL,16,Fthere was a need to "sweep out a lot
OL,17,Fof the historic, incoherent nonsense
OL,18,Fthat has been brought in under the
OL,19,Fguise of anti-racism".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FMr Farage said Mr Nowak was "treated
OL,7,Fin a way that meant an accusation of a
OL,8,Fracial slur was treated more seriously
OL,9,Fthan an act of murder" and said people
OL,10,Fshould react with "pure cold rage".
OL,12,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,13,Fgroup walked across town to the area
OL,14,Fof Portswood.
OL,16,FDemonstrators chanted "Henry, Henry"
OL,17,Fas the line of police were pelted with
OL,18,Fbricks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,7,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,8,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,9,Fback from the line they had been
OL,10,Fholding.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,13,Fthe scenes were "completely
OL,14,Funacceptable" and accused the
OL,15,Fdemonstrators of "hijacking this
OL,16,Ftragedy to stir up violence and
OL,17,Fdisorder".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FMr Nowak's killer, 23-year-old Vickrum
OL,7,FDigwa, told police attending the scene
OL,8,Fof the stabbing in Southampton on
OL,9,FDecember 3 2025 that he had been the
OL,10,Fvictim of a racist attack.
OL,12,FIn body-worn camera footage from the
OL,13,Fincident, a handcuffed Mr Nowak can be
OL,14,Fheard repeatedly saying: "I've been
OL,15,Fstabbed", to which an officer replies:
OL,16,F"Don't think you have, mate."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FMs Mahmood said: "The Nowak family
OL,7,Fmade a powerful call to us all
OL,8,Fyesterday to not let Henry's death be
OL,9,Fused to create further division,
OL,10,Fhatred or tension.
OL,12,F"There can be no justification for
OL,13,Fhijacking this tragedy to stir up
OL,14,Fviolence and disorder. Those
OL,15,Fresponsible can expect to face the
OL,16,Ffull force of the law.
OL,18,F"I thank the police who have tonight
OL,19,Fshown great bravery and calm in the
OL,20,Fface of disgraceful violence directed
OL,21,Fat them."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,7,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,8,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,9,Fknife with a 21cm blade prosecutors
OL,10,Fsaid was a kirpan, which he carried as
OL,11,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,13,FHe had previously been investigated by
OL,14,Fpolice in 2023 on suspicion of
OL,15,Fstealing ceremonial blades from a Sikh
OL,16,Ftemple in Southampton but no further
OL,17,Faction was taken.
OL,19,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,20,Freport on the case within the next
OL,21,Fthree months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780481194
OL,3,CAppeal for calm after protestors clash
OL,4,Cwith police in Southampton
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) said investigators are
OL,8,Fexamining a large amount of body-worn
OL,9,Fvideo as well as material presented
OL,10,Fduring Digwa's trial.
OL,12,FHampshire Police confirmed that one of
OL,13,Fthe officers involved in the case has
OL,14,Fresigned, while the other three are
OL,15,Fstill serving.
OL,17,FAll of them are being treated as
OL,18,Fwitnesses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
